Learn a simple fun visual magic trick! Get two different color @icebreakers mint packages, remove one label fully, then remove one half way and stick the other on to make a double layer flap. Now just secretly flip it with your fingers and bam! You can now do my original trick IceBreaker originally published lots of years ago. 

#reels #learn #fun #diy 

P.S. I hate this tiktok style as much as you but it’s succeeding only so gotta do it Fam. Forgive me for shhhhing a non existent person 😂

Christmas Magic 🎅🎄🪄 share to your story if you enjoy it! 

This project was probably the most logistically challenging thing I have ever worked on. Making a the gift that somebody is dreaming of appear on their doorstep moments after they simply mention it was without a doubt a Christmas miracle, all while on a FaceTime call! For a variety of other reasons this project nearly crushed me but watching it back does bring a smile to me every holiday season! I hope you enjoy it! 

#christmas #magic #holiday #reactions  p.s I am not sharing this as a reel so it will be interesting to see if it even gets 5 views 🙃
5 Years later this is still the best magic trick ever! 🌲♥️ @allistessel #christmas #love #proposal
